    ********************************************************************** -->

<!ELEMENT acclist - - (pnr+)>


<!--**********************************************************************
    * Define Element cdescs (List of Contact Descriptions) containing:-  *
    *  cdesc    - Mandatory Repeatable   contains contact, cdia, fin,    *
    *                                     tplus, tminus, sterm, coax,    *
    *                                     triax, module, block, shunt.   *
