<!ELEMENT cdescs - - (cdesc+)>


<!--**********************************************************************
    * Define Element cdesc (Contact Description) containing:-            *
    *  contact   - Mandatory Single       contains No Other Tags.        *
    *  cdia      - Optional  Single       contains Definition stored in  *
    *                                              entity %PCDATA;.      *
    *  fin       - Optional  Repeatable   contains Definition stored in  *
    *                                              entity %CM.PREFIN;.   *
    *  tplus     - Optional  Single       contains Definition stored in  *
    *                                              entity %PCDATA;.      *
    *  tminus    - Optional  Single       contains Definition stored in  *
    *                                              entity %PCDATA;.      *
    *  sterm     - Optional  Single       contains Definition stored in  *
    *                                              entity %PCDATA;.      *
    *  coax      - Optional  Single       contains Definition stored in  *
    *                                              entity %PCDATA;.      *
    *  triax     - Optional  Single       contains Definition stored in  *
    *                                              entity %PCDATA;.      *
    *  module    - Optional  Single       contains Definition stored in  *
    *                                              entity %PCDATA;.      *
    *  block     - Optional  Single       contains Definition stored in  *
    *                                              entity %PCDATA;.      *
    *  shunt     - Optional  Single       contains Definition stored in  *
    *                                              entity %PCDATA;.      *
    ********************************************************************** -->

<!ELEMENT cdesc - - (contact, cdia?, fin*, tplus?, tminus?, sterm?, coax?, 
                     triax?, module?, block?, shunt? )>


